{"tid":1233101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"612肺癌三期中槍大叔家人尋求協助","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T23:37:02.000Z","uid":146390,"like":377,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":255,"replies":[{"pid":"52df89242f5dececb3bb59142089f45b9e612f3f","tid":1233101,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳：<br />\n<br />\n患有肺癌三期的中槍大叔「老吳」，在6.12被警察用橡膠子彈射中後被捕，目前警方以非法集會罪控告他，但警方正申請搜查令搜屋，欲搜集更多證據改控暴動罪。<br />\r\n<br />\n我認識大叔的女兒，她現正公開呼籲尋找爸爸中槍一刻的影片，以證明警察濫用暴力。<br />\r\n<br />\n根據她轉述爸爸的話，當時他只是用粗口罵警察，手上並無武器，又不是在衝擊防線，警察根本在沒有受任何生命威脅的情況下開槍。<br />\r\n<br />\n目前大叔家人已找到人證，證明他中槍一刻的過程沒有使用暴力，但律師認為如有影片證供更為穩妥，現呼籲當日有拍攝影片的現場人士，如 6.12 下午 5 時 30 分，在添美道附近有拍攝到大叔中槍一刻，請聯絡 Francis 6159 6856。"},{"pid":"1aee81c03819aaf0a08e588bab8198b8d8e4a826","tid":1233101,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc3d9750f66bee9fad86c5f1aca410a882725354","tid":1233101,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dac071450076b121f2114a1da0e796ad673c38a5","tid":1233101,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51b7cee953ae5c301043c80023beaa334433eb73","tid":1233101,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:13.000Z","msg":"大家幫手"},{"pid":"5c6fa6d5f135be0fda721a65ac94f795a5d17804","tid":1233101,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"33f3020d3b1b2cadd0f67ca56e7f4ab66cd659e3","tid":1233101,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a2eb8e982c88d6330b1a6b7e8912739fc674ad11","tid":1233101,"uid":258703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0441e1a62a0f62b4e7b70767f2a9eeab