":1233101,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ed897b114e6a18143eee01fecc4a2d1321ccdc2","tid":1233101,"uid":142775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52df89242f5dececb3bb59142089f45b9e612f3f","tid":1233101,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳：<br />\n<br />\n患有肺癌三期的中槍大叔「老吳」，在6.12被警察用橡膠子彈射中後被捕，目前警方以非法集會罪控告他，但警方正申請搜查令搜屋，欲搜集更多證據改控暴動罪。<br />\r\n<br />\n我認識大叔的女兒，她現正公開呼籲尋找爸爸中槍一刻的影片，以證明警察濫用暴力。<br />\r\n<br />\n根據她轉述爸爸的話，當時他只是用粗口罵警察，手上並無武器，又不是在衝擊防線，警察根本在沒有受任何生命威脅的情況下開槍。<br />\r\n<br />\n目前大叔家人已找到人證，證明他中槍一刻的過程沒有使用暴力，但律師認為如有影片證供更為穩妥，現呼籲當日有拍攝影片的現場人士，如 6.12 下午 5 時 30 分，在添美道附近有拍攝到大叔中槍一刻，請聯絡 Francis 6159 6856。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c911338413f13b0c62e57cb87cc16eb14d0e6640","tid":1233101,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0153211bda5c182f48b457e471d506a53a14ee73","tid":1233101,"uid":74435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71329fe69ce6bdd5e1736a076f78300422181d66","tid":1233101,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8792113bb66b2463140829fabd25478fa9b46bf5","tid":1233101,"uid":262664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8da321f198550beb3b889cd4a1f944bbb9091aac","tid":1233101,"uid":45927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d338d627b473bf2fcf2847c34f378039920bdec","tid":1233101,"uid":74789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"554f58d0113dd2629fee669a2727b9aec17904ff","tid":1233101,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":