察，手上並無武器，又不是在衝擊防線，警察根本在沒有受任何生命威脅的情況下開槍。<br />\r\n<br />\n目前大叔家人已找到人證，證明他中槍一刻的過程沒有使用暴力，但律師認為如有影片證供更為穩妥，現呼籲當日有拍攝影片的現場人士，如 6.12 下午 5 時 30 分，在添美道附近有拍攝到大叔中槍一刻，請聯絡 Francis 6159 6856。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"致70後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233361</a>"},{"pid":"aaa05665fe239d50c29c551e2e48629fa5234b29","tid":1233101,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:09:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0513d59b2f9114db02af5206c92a441dcc24b3f","tid":1233101,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73893c96720ec36cbbc60d25ddf7dea7b8b15499","tid":1233101,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:23:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39d3eabe23955da3bf12303c96d79f8ab430eabd","tid":1233101,"uid":166243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16895060c191e7dc96733fb1af0c7aa2df2efc2c","tid":1233101,"uid":58584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:24:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7a365f8e9d602295b1842a277e5eea7adcfebdfa","tid":1233101,"uid":85776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d469223bd42a0e6737bbe69d2d7f4a07e27ee988","tid":1233101,"uid":166243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82d9552d4fdd6c66fc7c79a82b9624a2bbb7a727","tid":1233101,"uid":132893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1da3acda674850862b31e7f0b0783aada0ce0cc5","tid":1233101,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56c6afcf8d6c96a9bed00070f8a66badf828da8a","tid":1233101,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco